datasets.name: /ABS/Census/2021/TEND/tenure_rent/SA1
datasets.description: Percentage of households with tenure type 'rented'.

query.query_text: SELECT "SA1" as locale_id, "Rented" as "Renters" FROM public.ABS_2021_TEND_PC
query.filter: WHERE "SA1" in (SELECT sa1."SA1_CODE21" FROM abs_sa1s sa1 JOIN "AEC_CEDs" ced ON ST_Contains(ced.geometry, sa1.geometry) WHERE ced."Elect_div" in (%s));

datasets.context: Percentage of rented households in SA1 regions from 2021 Australian Census

datasets.name: /ABS/Census/2021/RELP/Islam/SA1
datasets.description: Percentage of households selecting religion: Islam.

query.query_text: SELECT "SA1" as locale_id, "Islam" as "Islam" FROM public.ABS_2021_RELP_PC
query.filter: WHERE "SA1" in (SELECT sa1."SA1_CODE21" FROM abs_sa1s sa1 JOIN "AEC_CEDs" ced ON ST_Intersects(ced.geometry, sa1.geometry) WHERE ced."Elect_div" in (%s));

datasets.context: Percentage of Islamic households in SA1 regions from 2021 Australian Census

datasets.name: /ABS/Census/2021/EDUC/Bachelors/SA1
datasets.description: Percentage of people with bachelors degree or higher.

query.query_text: SELECT "SA1" as locale_id, abs_2021_heap_pc."Bachelor Degree Level" + abs_2021_heap_pc."Postgraduate Degree Level" + abs_2021_heap_pc."Graduate Diploma and Graduate Certificate Level" as "Bachelors" from public.abs_2021_heap_pc
query.filter: WHERE "SA1" in ( SELECT sa1."SA1_CODE21" FROM abs_sa1s sa1 JOIN "AEC_CEDs" ced ON (ST_Contains(ced.geometry, sa1.geometry) OR ST_Overlaps(ced.geometry, sa1.geometry)) WHERE ced."Elect_div" in (%s))
